name: Neptune's Endless Waves
description:
Neptune sits in the 11th house of community and good fortune making harmonious aspects to either edge of the horizon, uniting self and other in inspiration, intuition, sublime experiences, and the deepest foundations of the sky and soul.

This work is about the incredible, unending brilliance of the Tezos NFT community and its incredible people overflowing with support, joy, and collaboration with the Moon configured positively to Mercury and Saturn, planets of communication and structure.

Source Photography Credits: NASA, L. Sromovsky, and P. Fry (University of Wisconsin-Madison); NASA, ESA, A. Simon (NASA Goddard Space Flight Center), and M.H. Wong and A. Hsu (University of California, Berkeley)
